<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٦٤٧ - عَنْ هِشَامِ بْنِ حَسَّانَ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«ثَلَاثٌ لِلْبِكْرِ، وَلَيْلَتَانِ لِلثَّيِّبِ»</span>. عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٢٣٧⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٠٦٤٨ - عَنْ يُونُسَ، عَنِ الْحَسَنِ مِثْلَهُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>